      <title>利率上升推动三菱日联金融集团利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mufg-profit-beats-estimates-with-tailwind-from-rising-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三菱日联金融集团公布季度利润超过预期，其与规模较小的竞争对手瑞穗金融集团一样，均指出日本利率上升推动贷款收入增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mufg-profit-beats-estimates-with-tailwind-from-rising-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田、日产将在软件、电池和电动汽车技术方面展开合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/honda-nissan-to-team-up-on-software-batteries-ev-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司和日产汽车公司同意在软件、电池和其他电动汽车相关技术方面进行合作，以节省成本并在未来更好地竞争，尤其是在中国等销量下滑的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/honda-nissan-to-team-up-on-software-batteries-ev-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥运会合作伙伴 Atos 在重组中亏损严重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/olympics-partner-atos-reports-heavy-losses-amid-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于巨额减值费用和客户需求疲软给这家陷入困境的法国 IT 公司带来压力，Atos SE 报告今年上半年亏损 19.4 亿欧元（21 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/olympics-partner-atos-reports-heavy-losses-amid-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>威立雅利润因废物和水务服务需求增长而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/veolia-profit-rises-on-growing-demand-for-waste-water-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威立雅环境集团上半年盈利因服务需求增长及成本削减而上涨 10%，使公司有望实现全年利润目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/veolia-profit-rises-on-growing-demand-for-waste-water-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星芯片主管警告称，除非做出改变，否则将陷入“恶性循环”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/samsung-chips-boss-warns-of-vicious-cycle-if-it-doesn-t-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司芯片业务领导人在上任数月后向员工发出了一份异常严厉的备忘录，警告称，如果不改革企业文化，这家韩国最大的公司就有可能陷入“恶性循环”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/samsung-chips-boss-warns-of-vicious-cycle-if-it-doesn-t-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默克集团预计人工智能繁荣将推动半导体业务反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/merck-sees-rebound-for-semiconductor-business-amid-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[默克公司表示，在人工智能浪潮的推动下，其半导体业务已到达转折点，并提供了有关该德国公司上调盈利预测的更多细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/merck-sees-rebound-for-semiconductor-business-amid-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>打击中国学生引发对英国科技雄心的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-university-crackdown-on-chinese-students-harms-country-s-tech-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些商界领袖和学者担心，保护大学免受间谍活动侵害的运动会使该国的科学抱负面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-university-crackdown-on-chinese-students-harms-country-s-tech-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:19:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
